This installation was performed on Ubuntu Linux x86 64bit.

Install dependencies:
  apt-get install libxml2-dev git-core libshp-dev libglib2.0-dev

Adapt osm2shp.cfg to your needs. You need to recompile the program after
changing osm2shp.cfg.

Run make to compile sourcecode:
  make

Run binary:
  mkdir shapefiles
  ./osm2shp -d shapefiles/ map.osm
